cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with face recognition systems and image synthesis, which are both topics within computer vision (cs.CV). The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) is a key aspect of the proposed method, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of semantic labels and identity extraction, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), respectively. Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method in cross-spectral face matching, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR).
